Shivering Touch
Necromancy [cold]
Level: Cleric 3, Sorceror/Wizard 3
Components: V, S
Casting Time: 1 Standard Action
Range: Touch
Target: Creature Touched
Duration: 1 round/level
Saving Throw: None
Spell Resistance: Yes

On a succesful melee attack, you instantly suck the heat from the target's body, rendering it numb. The target takes 3d6 points of Dexterity damage. Creatures with the cold subtype are immune to the effects of Shivering Touch.
